<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hardly-ever">hardly ever</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-almost-never">1.<strong>很少；几乎从不 (almost never)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Sometimes I think you watch too much TV. 
有时我觉得你看电视太多了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Oh I hardly ever watch TV.
哦，我很少看电视</p></div></div>